      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, ideal for a dedicated project or as a parts donor. The engine has a significant internal knock and multiple active oil leaks that will require a complete teardown or replacement to be roadworthy again. The body shows visible wear and the interior has seen better days, though some trim pieces remain salvageable. Please expect a vehicle that requires towing and a substantial mechanical overhaul.",
