    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really wonderful shape. It runs super smoothly and has been well-loved throughout the time I've owned it. I'm looking for a nice, easy sale, so I've priced it to move quickly! Feel free to reach out with any questions at all\u2014I'm more than happy to chat and show you around the car!",
