    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with six individual throttle bodies and a high-precision 6-speed manual gearbox. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a complete VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral G-loads. The variable M differential lock provides exceptional exit-corner traction, while the suspension maintains its factory-spec responsiveness with forged aluminum components. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the drivetrain is optimized for peak performance and linear power delivery.",
